
& dodge_maneuver
 
 >> Help: Dodge Maneuver (Advantage)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Type 'dodge' to toggle this advantage on and off.
 
 +2 BTH to your enemy's melee attack rolls.
 You cannot perform melee attacks while this advantage is engaged.
 
 Result: It is harder for an enemy to hit you with melee attacks, and you
 can only use weapons while in combat.
 
 For a detailed look at this advantage, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
